org.apache.juneau.http

Class HttpResources

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.juneau.http.HttpResources

  • public class HttpResources
extends Object
    Standard predefined HTTP resources.

    Resources are simply HttpEntity objects with arbitrary additional headers.
